    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>It seems you've been led astray, haven't you?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/9bef6aacdd4fc8c51429ee9979ad3498.poster.avif?t=1764853252\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/9bef6aacdd4fc8c51429ee9979ad3498.webm?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/9bef6aacdd4fc8c51429ee9979ad3498.mp4?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >April 26, 2003</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You arrive in <strong>Aerie Vista</strong> to finally meet your online friends in person. What starts as a simple trip soon takes a dark turn. When a trip to the bookstore leads you all into a gateway to the other world, you find yourselves in an alternate realm filled with mystery and danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/c91967b40b4e440d9f7b79eae8f69053.poster.avif?t=1764853252\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/c91967b40b4e440d9f7b79eae8f69053.webm?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/c91967b40b4e440d9f7b79eae8f69053.mp4?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a Soultracer, you're able to separate your soul from your body, allowing you to navigate this strange new world where you’ll encounter cryptic puzzles, eerie environments, and indescribable horrors. You will meet new faces along the way, and it will be up to you to decide whom you can trust. With its nostalgic  PS2-inspired graphics, Soultracer offers a thrilling experience reminiscent of classic survival horror games. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/c4212f1fd43a000c90db98ee9bdc1804.poster.avif?t=1764853252\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/c4212f1fd43a000c90db98ee9bdc1804.webm?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/c4212f1fd43a000c90db98ee9bdc1804.mp4?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Got souls to spend?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/9a834615514cad64bdb2d69dac688f78.poster.avif?t=1764853252\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/9a834615514cad64bdb2d69dac688f78.webm?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/9a834615514cad64bdb2d69dac688f78.mp4?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be sure to speak with the bartender! She'll have what you need for a fair <strong>price</strong>. She will always give you some advice in case the road ahead is not clear enough. Don't forget to regularly check what she has new in stock, you'll need all the help you can get. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Return To Survival Horror:</strong> Experience a game designed with the visual and atmospheric style of  PS2-era survival horror titles. Heavily inspired by Resident Evil, Silent Hill, Haunting Ground and Alone in the Dark. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Mysterious World:</strong> Explore a parallel world with intriguing environments and cryptic challenges that blur the line between reality and nightmare. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/68bd18893f01d555bda52dc5be20a5f2.poster.avif?t=1764853252\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/68bd18893f01d555bda52dc5be20a5f2.webm?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/68bd18893f01d555bda52dc5be20a5f2.mp4?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Engaging Story:</strong> Follow a gripping narrative as you and your friends uncover the dark secrets of this new world. Each of you plays a crucial role in piecing together the mystery that binds this world to the unknown.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Dynamic NPC Interactions:</strong> Meet a range of NPCs who may offer guidance, assistance, or present new challenges as you progress. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Challenging Enemies:</strong> Enemies pose an immediate threat, don't let your guard down. Featuring boss fights that require both brains &amp; brawn, thread very carefully. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/de5cc42af5048e8ef83baa59797c15c7.poster.avif?t=1764853252\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/de5cc42af5048e8ef83baa59797c15c7.webm?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/de5cc42af5048e8ef83baa59797c15c7.mp4?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Weapons &amp; Items:</strong> Manage your resources via your inventory. There's a wide variety of different weapons, each one more efficient for certain tasks at hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/cd18053b0fa3a58fb8ac24000ee9c5d8.poster.avif?t=1764853252\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/cd18053b0fa3a58fb8ac24000ee9c5d8.webm?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/cd18053b0fa3a58fb8ac24000ee9c5d8.mp4?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Puzzles:</strong> Always think outside the box if you wish to survive the night. Your skills will be tested. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Replayability:</strong> Everything is not always going to be the same! Curious on what would happen if you did things differently? Then you can always choose differently next time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Voice Acting:</strong> Each character you meet is brought to life thanks to talented voice actors. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Original Soundtrack:</strong> Original musical scores composed for Soultracer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Secrets &amp; Extras:</strong> Rewards for completing certain milestones within the other world. These may range from weapons to clothing. Can you find them all? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you help your friends survive the darkness that lies beyond and escape this world? Your quest in <strong>Soultracer</strong> will test your courage, wit, and resilience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/c3278e1e886fb59539df963b65d632c1.poster.avif?t=1764853252\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/c3278e1e886fb59539df963b65d632c1.webm?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155760/extras/c3278e1e886fb59539df963b65d632c1.mp4?t=1764853252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You're the only one who can.</strong></h2>",
